==  Variables ==

=== Global ===

$iscsi_target_targetname => the name of the iscsi box
$iscsi_target_ip => ip of the iscsi box

=== Per client ===

$iscsi_initiatorname => initator name
iscsi_target_pwd => target password
$iscsi_initiator_pwd => initiator password
